OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud with some breaks, and patchy
OL,7,Fmist, fog or low cloud likely to
OL,8,Fdevelop in places. Winds remaining
OL,9,Flight, breezy along the coast. Feeling
OL,10,Fcooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FBright or sunny spells but
OL,13,Fturning cloudier through the evening
OL,14,Fas scattered showers move south, with
OL,15,Fa cooler northerly breeze arriving
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
