OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and mostly dry,
OL,7,Falthough isolated, mainly light
OL,8,Fshowers still possible. Cooler
OL,9,Fmidweek, with patchy overnight rural
OL,10,Fgrass frost possible, turning milder
OL,11,Fagain later. Winds generally light.
